hopobject.body: Which university are you at? how much does generic viagra cost at walmart So while it's all well and good to fawn over the Hyperloop – and imagine what zooming over California in a series of tubes would be like – it's worth remembering that there are plenty of ways to make America a much better and more pleasant place to travel without building the train of the future. We just need to invest in actually building some of the trains (and other transit systems) of today.
